{
  "stem": "13313.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember-- I remember that first of all, we all had to wear the yellow Star of David with the words-- I think, three languages, or at least two-- the word 'Jew' in Dutch, which was 'Jood,' J-O-O-D, and then 'Juif' for the French part, J-U-I-F.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This you had to wear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were told that not wearing this and getting caught, there would be a severe penalty.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this is the first thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sewing on the yellow star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Obviously, we're all walking around with stars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next thing I know was that the-- all Jewish enterprises had to have a sign on-- on their window saying in three languages-- German, Dutch, and French-- Jewish Enterprise.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] These were the three languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they would be identified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- so part of the propaganda was to boycott Jewish enterprises.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So therefore, all of a sudden, our business was also targeted because of that sign.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Next thing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Next thing, we were-- the main mode of transportation was streetcars.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And most street-- and some streetcars had a-- just one car, and then some had a second car attached.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So then, the next thing was the Jews were restricted with the stars only on the first platform of the second car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So, a lot of cars have no second car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We just couldn't use public transportation anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a kind of segregation of transportation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After that, curfew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed outside of their homes after a certain time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was either 7 o'clock or 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And all these things gradually changed everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, we're still going to the same school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we didn't go outside much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in school, there was no problem, because we're all Jewish kids in that particular-- in Tachkemoni.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
